<!--{{FCC ST|10/11/2017|indexme.}}--> FCC documents suggest that either a QCA8072 or a QCA8075 will be used :for the switch and a Toshiba THGBMDG5D1LBAIT might be used instead :of the Samsung eMMC shown in the FCC internal photos.
The biggest difference between this version and the previous [[Google Wifi (NLS-1304-25)|NLS-1304-25]] :is that the unused ZigBee hardware is removed.
